###register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"ali@yahoo.com",
  "password":"123456"
}


###login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"ali@yahoo.com",
  "password":"123456"
}

###logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout


###refreshToken
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refreshToken


